Subject: File System scan has errored out 5 weeks in a row
Description: I have attached the error messages that we've received from last week's scans.  The messages are on different folders every week, but errors, nonetheless.  Please assist.
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
FS scans are erroring every week due to rpc timeout and some file path security descriptor errors

[Root Cause]
Had to do with the timeout minutes and the folder issue is due to a new contractor including the hash in the folder name, rendering it too long.
